{"tid":1864253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早產嬰父母：林鄭藉孩子之名情緒勒索可恥","createTime":"2020-02-05T13:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T18:14:04.000Z","uid":125168,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72fe217ac2c6baf27ee8b2008b3b201d5cfd9c08","tid":1864253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"【醫護罷工】早產嬰父母實名聯署聲援 斥林鄭藉孩子之名情緒勒索可恥<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200205&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60564021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200205%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60564021&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=5162fa3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200205%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60564021&h=64988407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200205&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60564021</a>"},{"pid":"38f06344dcd4dc93448e9ab6f160415198f39b0d","tid":1864253,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"根本全世界都支持醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720084795fceab9f3229100ac1db2f9cab408b07","tid":1864253,"uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥昨稱，醫護罷工令深切治療部的新生嬰兒未能得到適切照顧。今日最少有203位曾入住新生嬰兒深切治療部（NICU）的早產嬰父母聯署公開信，譴責林鄭的言論誤導及可恥，表明支持醫護以罷工救港，反斥政府未能有效防疫，「卻以我們孩子的名義道德勒索前線醫護，抹黑他們的專業操守」；部份聯署者更貼出子女留院時的照片作證，又感謝醫護人員當時悉心照顧其子女。"},{"pid":"f5ebebf5c5a4594a5788d45742b60bb1efbe2938","tid":1864253,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"他們在信中直言，十分了解及支持醫護罷工，明白醫護並非逃避責任及害怕感染，而是為了爭取全面封關以拯救港人。"},{"pid":"709e6e818276963e59a86846722c29fdae13a35b","tid":1864253,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"777人渣"},{"pid":"4de98efb69d603226c67f6e394197bd5c10b0a3